{"tid":765843,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Zombie Boy 生日前夕自殺身亡","createTime":"2018-08-03T06:00:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T10:39:43.000Z","uid":72739,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"22f8d4ea23eaa23a11b171f4f22e6ec96a06597b","tid":765843,"uid":72739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T06:00:22.000Z","msg":"曾演出Lady GaGa歌曲MV《Born This Way》的加拿大模特兒Rick Genest，前日被發現在加拿大蒙特利爾家中自殺身亡，終年32歲。<br />\n<br />\nRick Genest於15歲時發現罹患腦瘤，一年後他戰勝病魔，亦同時愛上紋身，全身都紋上不同紋身，亦因將臉紋到像骷髏頭一樣，因而被稱為「Zombie Boy」。於七年前，Rick Genest 與Lady GaGa合作《Born This Way》而為人熟悉，他亦有參與電影拍攝，包括奇洛在的《浪魂47》（47 Ronin）。<br />\nRick一生都跟身體與心理上的病魔戰鬥，將於本月七日生日的他，於33歲生日前夕結束生命，而他死前最後留是一張從水井底向上望的照片。<br />\nGaGa得知Rick離世後亦受到打擊，留言悼念：「我們必須更加努力地改變文化，令心理健康放更受到關注，消除我們不能談論的忌諱。 如果你正在遭同樣苦痛，請立即致電朋友或家人，我們必須互相拯救。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180803/small/1533267039_e991.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180803%2Fsmall%2F1533267039_e991.jpg&h=5d914577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRick因全身都有紋身，被稱為「Zombie Boy」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180803/small/1533265854_e4e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180803%2Fsmall%2F1533265854_e4e9.jpg&h=182ba53c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLady GaGa得知Rick死訊後留言悼念。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180803/small/1533265997_dd69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180803%2Fsmall%2F1533265997_dd69.jpg&h=05aaa70c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRick最後一次留言是從水井底向上望的陰沉照片。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180803/small/1533267039_ed4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180803%2Fsmall%2F1533267039_ed4b.jpg&h=3b9d5bfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRick曾演出《浪魂47》。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288"},{"pid":"5e6966479383e5bf9937ae431c1dc08e7824eaa7","tid":765843,"uid":72739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T06:03:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180803/large/1533265854_e4e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180803%2Flarge%2F1533265854_e4e9.jpg&h=bbda1865&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180803/large/1533265997_dd69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180803%2Flarge%2F1533265997_dd69.jpg&h=a65b1a55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180803/58518210\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180803%2F58518210&d=3qbCDYsWA4zLZmsCRWad2JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=7f18bee3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180803%2F58518210&h=b3256f21\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180803/58518210</a>"},{"pid":"4b8b4509aa6f815a09747b225238d7ea2b3932fe","tid":765843,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T06:04:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a051a220e1ab6916a1ed2f477c661e850e92132","tid":765843,"uid":63505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T06:04:44.000Z","msg":"好似佢未紋之前都幾靚仔"},{"pid":"c6e9ea64b656dc74ec7548d93b734778013f712b","tid":765843,"uid":72739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu